Even Better Version

Instead of a solid film…

Create a microcellular foam skin.

Millions of microscopic closed bubbles.

Exactly like tiny bubble wrap.

Each bubble contains air.

That could reduce heat transfer dramatically while remaining soft enough to walk naturally.

